ertifiedawards/search.aspx ] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214044701/http://www.bpi.co.uk/certifiedawards/search.aspx |date=14 February 2012 }}</ref>\n|\n*US: 234,000<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/502934/estelle-returns-fresh-off-a-smash-single-and-breakup-with-all-of|magazine= Billboard|title=Estelle Returns, Fresh Off A Smash Single and Breakup, with 'All of Me'|first= Richard|last=Smirke|date= 2 March 2012|accessdate=24 August 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[All of Me (Estelle album)|All of Me]]''\n|\n*Released: 28 February 2012\n*Label: Atlantic\n*Formats: CD, digital download\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 28 || 9 || \u2014\n|\n|\n*US: 77,000<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211084522/http://hitsdailydouble.com/new_album_releases |archivedate=11 February 2015 |url=http://hitsdailydouble.com/new_album_releases |title=Upcoming Releases |website=Hits Daily Double |publisher=HITS Digital Ventures }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[True Romance (Estelle album)|True Romance]]''\n|\n*Released: 17 February 2015\n*Label: 1980 Records/[[BMG Rights Management|BMG]]\n*Formats: CD, digital download\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 31 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Lovers Rock (Estelle album)|Lovers Rock]]''\n|\n*Released: 7 September 2018\n*Label: 1980 Records/VP Records\n*Formats: CD, digital download\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|''Lovers Rock'' did not enter the US Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums Chart, but did chart at 18 on the R&B Album Sales Chart.<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.billboard.com/biz/charts/2018-09-22/randb-album-sales|title=R&B Album Sales chart|publisher=Billboard Biz|date=September 22, 2018|accessdate=April 12, 2019}}</ref>}} || 2\n|\n|\n|-\n|colspan=\"15\" style=\"font-size:9