: Estelle \u2018Love & Happiness, Vol. 3: How Stella Got Her Groove Back\u2019 |magazine=[[Vibe (magazine)|Vibe.com]]|accessdate=31 July 2014}}</ref>\n*Label: 1980 Records/BMG\n*Formats: digital download\n|}\n\n==Singles==\n===As lead artist===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of singles, with selected chart positions, showing year released and album name\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:16em;\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"11\" | Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:12em;\" | [[List of music recording certifications|Certifications]]\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" | Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"|[[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br><ref name=uk/><ref name=\"Tracklisting\">{{cite web|url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/CLUK_E.HTM |title=Zobbel.de \u2013 Chart Log UK: E-40 \u2013 E-Z Rollers |publisher=Zobbel.de |accessdate=8 February 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gfy0Ug5r?url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/CLUK_E.HTM |archivedate=17 May 2013 |df=dmy }}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"|[[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br><ref name=aus>{{cite web|url=http://australian-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Estelle|title=Australian Charts > Estelle|publisher=australian-charts.com Hung Medien|accessdate=9 July 2011}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"|[[\u00d63 Austria Top 40|AUT]]<br><ref name=aut/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"|[[Canadian Hot 100|CAN]]<br><ref>http://www.billboard.com/artist/301898/estelle/chart?f=793</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"|[[GfK Entertainment Charts|GER]]<br><ref>Peak positions for singles Germany:\n*For \"American Boy\": {{cite web|url=http://musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/Estelle+Feat.West%2CKanye/single|title=Chartverfolgung / Estelle feat. West, Kanye / Single|language=G